---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Platform Support - Open Cleaner RN">
	<main>
		<h1>Platform Support</h1>
		
		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Supported Platforms</h2>
			<p>
				Open Cleaner RN is a cross-platform application that runs natively on:
			</p>
			<div class="platform-grid">
				<div class="platform-card">
					<h3>Windows</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Windows 10 and newer</li>
						<li>64-bit architecture</li>
						<li>MSI installer package</li>
						<li>Auto-updates supported</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="platform-card">
					<h3>macOS</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>macOS 10.15 and newer</li>
						<li>Intel and Apple Silicon</li>
						<li>DMG package</li>
						<li>Notarized for security</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="platform-card">
					<h3>Linux</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Ubuntu 20.04 and newer</li>
						<li>Other major distributions</li>
						<li>AppImage, DEB, RPM</li>
						<li>System tray support</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Build Configurations</h2>
			<p>
				Each platform has specific build configurations and requirements:
			</p>
			
			<h3>Windows Requirements</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Visual Studio Build Tools</li>
				<li>Windows SDK</li>
				<li>WiX Toolset for MSI creation</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>macOS Requirements</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Xcode Command Line Tools</li>
				<li>Apple Developer Certificate (for distribution)</li>
				<li>Universal binary support</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Linux Requirements</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Build essentials package</li>
				<li>GTK development libraries</li>
				<li>AppImage tools</li>
				<li>RPM and DEB build tools</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Automated Builds</h2>
			<p>
				Our GitHub Actions workflow automatically handles:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Cross-platform compilation</li>
				<li>Package creation for each platform</li>
				<li>Code signing and notarization</li>
				<li>Artifact uploading</li>
			</ul>
			<pre><code>Platform-specific artifacts are built using matrix strategy:
- Windows: .msi
- macOS: .dmg (Intel + Apple Silicon)
- Linux: .AppImage, .deb, .rpm</code></pre>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Testing</h2>
			<p>
				Each platform build undergoes:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Automated testing on CI</li>
				<li>Platform-specific integration tests</li>
				<li>Installation testing</li>
				<li>Update mechanism verification</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Known Limitations</h2>
			<table>
				<thead>
					<tr>
						<th>Platform</th>
						<th>Limitation</th>
						<th>Workaround</th>
					</tr>
				</thead>
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td>Windows</td>
						<td>Requires admin for first run</td>
						<td>Use installer flags</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>macOS</td>
						<td>Gatekeeper warning</td>
						<td>Notarization process</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>Linux</td>
						<td>Varied system tray support</td>
						<td>Fallback to app indicator</td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		max-width: 900px;
	}
	.content-section {
		margin: 2rem 0;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		background-color: #23262d;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	h2 {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	h3 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		margin: 1rem 0;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}
	.platform-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}
	.platform-card {
		background-color: #1a1a1a;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 25%);
	}
	pre {
		background-color: #1a1a1a;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		overflow-x: auto;
		margin: 1rem 0;
	}
	code {
		font-family: monospace;
		white-space: pre;
	}
	ul {
		margin-left: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	li {
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
	}
	table {
		width: 100%;
		border-collapse: collapse;
		margin: 1rem 0;
	}
	th, td {
		padding: 0.75rem;
		text-align: left;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}
	th {
		background-color: #1a1a1a;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}
	tr:nth-child(even) {
		background-color: #1a1a1a;
	}
</style> 